        "starterCode": "def mock_spark_job(data):\n    print(\"Original Data:\", data)\n    \n    # 1. Map Phase (Applies function to every element)\n    # Square each number\n    mapped = list(map(lambda x: ___, data))\n    print(\"Mapped Data:\", mapped)\n    \n    # 2. Reduce Phase (Aggregates list into a single value)\n    from functools import reduce\n    # Sum all numbers\n    result = reduce(lambda a, b: ___, mapped)\n    \n    return result\n\nbig_data = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]\nfinal_result = mock_spark_job(big_data)\nprint(\"Final Reduced Result:\", final_result)",
