        "instructions": "## Task: Age Classifier\n1. Create a variable `age` set to `16`\n2. If age < 13, print `'Child'`\n3. Elif age < 18, print `'Teenager'`\n4. Elif age < 65, print `'Adult'`\n5. Else print `'Senior'`",
